INSERT INTO `bc_download_data` VALUES('27','<section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">为了积极推动儿童常见疾病的诊疗筛查，提升治疗效果，降低患儿、家属及医疗机构和社会负担，同时促进儿童常见疾病筛查最新相关科研成果的临床转化，响应《健康儿童行动提升计划（2021—2025年）》的号召，共同推动提升儿童健康服务能力和水平，努力为儿童提供连续、全面的儿童健康服务，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">北京英诺特生物技术股份有限公司与广东省钟南山医学基金会基于双方在各自业务领域的优势和发展潜力，共同设立“广东省钟南山医学基金会—英诺特健康专项基金”，</span>广东省钟南山医学基金会于12月15日通过官方网站进行了项目公示。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><p><img src=\"/uploadfile/2021/1222/20211222660978.jpg\" title=\"20211222660978.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20211216133436.jpg\"/></p><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><section></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">世界卫生组织资料显示，2016年肺炎造成92万＜5岁儿童死亡，其中98%来自发展中国家。肺炎也是当前我国＜5岁儿童死亡的主要原因之一，其中绝大部分儿童肺炎为社区获得性肺炎(CAP)。</strong>社区获得性肺炎中的重症难治性支原体肺炎和腺病毒肺炎等遗留的气道闭塞，是造成儿童患慢性气道疾病、影响生命质量的重要原因。另一方面，儿童过敏性疾病发病率呈逐年上升趋势，受到社会公众与医务工作者的广泛关注。<br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">中国城市婴幼儿过敏性疾病流行病学调查提示，40.9％的0~24月龄婴幼儿家长自报孩子曾出现或正表现有过敏性疾病症状，0~24月龄婴幼儿过敏性疾病总患病率为12.3％。作为儿科常见慢性疾病，过敏性疾病已严重影响患儿的生活质量和身体健康，同时在临床实践过程中，仍存在认识不清晰、就诊不及时、漏诊误诊多、治疗不规范等许多问题，亟待社会各界共同努力解决。呼吸道感染、过敏及相关疾病是影响儿童群体生命健康和生活质量的第一大类疾病，并对患儿预后、机体及后期成长造成长远影响，基于儿童的特殊性，该类疾病也给患儿父母及全社会造成较重的社会负担。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">随着《国务院关于实施健康中国行动的意见》、《“健康中国 2030” 规划纲要》、《“十四五”卫生健康规划》、《健康儿童行动提升计划（2021—2025年）》等政策文件的陆续出台，为我国儿童相关疾病的规范化诊疗指明了工作方向。在此背景下，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">北京英诺特生物技术有限公司与广东省钟南山医学基金会共同设立“广东省钟南山医学基金会——英诺特健康专项基金”，该专项基金聘请国内知名儿科呼吸道专家申昆玲和孙宝清教授、郑跃杰教授分别担任专项基金副主任委员和委员。</span></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">本基金立足于自愿，以公益为基本原则，致力于提高社会各界对儿童呼吸道感染、过敏等相关疾病的就诊、诊断和治疗，同时本基金还将支持儿童呼吸道疾病的临床研究与成果转化，本基金成立后将开展如下工作：</strong></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(71, 193, 168);\">&nbsp;1&nbsp;</span></strong></span>&nbsp;开展儿童呼吸道与过敏相关疾病的科普教育，促进社会各界对疾病的正确认识，提高就诊率，并增加患者及家长的防患意识</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(71, 193, 168); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;2&nbsp;</span></strong>&nbsp;推广儿童呼吸道与过敏相关疾病诊断和治疗方面的最新进展，提高就诊与治疗的规范性</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(71, 193, 168); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;3&nbsp;</span></strong>&nbsp;加强对儿童呼吸道与过敏相关疾病诊断、治疗的基础研究，促进学术成果的转换并最终服务临床</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(71, 193, 168); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;4&nbsp;</span></strong>&nbsp;开展对基层医院尤其是贫困地区的专家义诊，并对贫困患儿进行相关资助</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/uploadfile/2021/1222/20211222724613.jpg\" title=\"20211222724613.jpg\" alt=\"公司文化.jpg\"/></p></section><section><section><br/></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">北京英诺特生物技术股份有限公司</strong></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">一家专注于POCT快速诊断产品研发、生产和销售的国家高新技术企业。公司专注于儿童健康领域各类疾病检测技术的探索与成果转化，在儿童呼吸道感染、肠道感染、过敏检测等各类儿童疾病的筛查检测方面积极布局，致力于推进我国儿童常见疾病规范诊治，推动儿童健康事业高质量发展。公司为我国呼吸道病原体联检的领先企业之一，拥有呼吸道病原体的系列检测产品。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">公司核心产品呼吸道全血五联检--肺炎支原体IgM抗体、肺炎衣原体IgM抗体、呼吸道合胞病毒IgM 抗体、腺病毒IgM抗体、柯萨奇病毒B组IgM抗体联合检测试剂盒 （胶体金法），</span>可以帮助临床对最常见呼吸道病原体进行快速筛查，协助制定精准的治疗方案，具有组合合理、操作方便、结果快速等众多优势，深受广大临床一线的认可，已在北京儿童医院、北京儿研所、上海儿童医学中心、复旦大学附属儿科医院等全国知名儿童医院得到广泛的应用。</p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/uploadfile/2021/1222/20211222599226.png\" title=\"20211222599226.png\" alt=\"微信图片_20211216134338.png\"/></p></section><section><section><br/></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">广东省钟南山医学基金会</strong></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">广东省民政厅批准成立的3A级慈善组织。业务范围包括资助医学学术交流；资助奖励医学相关科学研究、教育、创新研究及技术推广应用、科技成果转化；开展医学科普健康教育、编著医学图书期刊；开展扶贫济困、救病助医、资助养老、抗击疫情、健康促进等公益慈善活动。</p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>','0','','0','0','','0','','1','','','','','','array (
